    "alignment_title": "Alignment Report",
    "alignment_text": "Ensure koj lus qhia hits mark. This report automatically cross-references koj tsimd khoom sivs against Common Core Standards thiab UDL Guidelines, identifying strengths thiab gaps.\n### AKuv Standards Nrhiaver\n• **Smart Nrhiav**: Enter a lub ntsiab los yog skill thiab AKuv suggests matching CCSS, NGSS, los yog TEKS standards.\n• **AKuv Consultation**: Tau strategy advice on how koj content ntxivresses specific standards.\n• **Multi-Framework**: Supports Common Core ELA/Math, NGSS, thiab state-specific frameworks.\n### Alignment Tshawbs\n• **CAST UDL Guidelines**: Tshawbs rau Engagement, Reprexa tagation, thiab Action/Expression.\n• **Standards Verification**: Cross-reference nrog Common Core, NGSS, los yog State Standards.\n• **Gap Kev Tshawb**: Kuvdentifies missing elements los yog pebak cov point in koj phiaj xwm kawm.\n• **Suggestions**: Actionable advice rau improve alignment.\n### Pro Lus Pab\n• Siv Gap Kev Tshawb rau justify khoom siv requests los yog co-planning sij hawm rau administration.\n### UDL Connection\n• **Action & Expression**: Enhance capacity rau monitoring kev vam meej (Guideline 6.4) by establishing tshem lub hom phiajs thiab ua tau criteria.",
