    "fullpack_title": "Full Pack",
    "fullpack_text": "universal 'Yooj Yim Button' rau instant, high-quality content generation. Zoo Tag Nrho rau xib fwbs, niam txivs, thiab self-guided learners, this cuab yeej tsims every khoom siv in sequence nrog intelligent AKuv configuration.\n### Smart Automation\n• **Auto-Configuration**: AKuv analyzes koj cov ntawv thiab intelligently configures optimal cov teebtingss rau every cuab yeej.\n• **Concov ntawv-Aware**: Ensures quizzes, scaffqubs, thiab games are zoo tag nrholy aligned rau cov ntawv complexity thiab themes.\n• **Custom Khoom Siv Suav**: Xaiv 'Auto' (AKuv picks esxa tagials) los yog 'All' (full 13-khoom siv suite).\n### Tsimd Khoom Sivs\nBatch tsims up rau 13 khoom sivs in intelligent order:\n• **Kev Tshawb** (thawj) ? Phau Ntawv Txhais Lus ? Theemed Cov Ntawv ? Visual Daim Duab\n• **Outline** ? FAQ ? Xa Tagence Frames ? Sij Hawmline\n• **Persona Kuvnterview** ? Concept Sort ? Brainstorm ? Quiz\n• **Phiaj Xwm Kawm** (tom kawg, sivs all prior khoom sivs rau concov ntawv)\n### Mode Adaptation\n• **Xib Fwb Mode**: Full educator khoom sivs nrog pedagogical guidance.\n• **Tub Ntxhais Kawm Mode**: Self-study materials nrog embedded supports.\n• **Niam Txiv Mode**: Family-friendly guides rau home learning.\n### Pro Lus Pab\nEnter custom instructions before nyeming Full Pack•AKuv distributes them intelligently across all tsimd khoom sivs!\n### UDL Connection\n• **Action & Expression**: Streamlines khoom siv creation (Guideline 5) by automatically generating mullus pable formats los ntawm a single source.",
    "utils_title": "Accessibility Hub",
