    "onboarding_hint": "💡 Nyem <strong>?</strong> anysij hawm rau kev pab!",
    "header_ai_backend": "AKuv Rov Qabend Configuration:\nHloov los yog xaiv koj preferred AKuv provider globally (p.t., Google Gemini, Anthropic Claude, QhibAKuv, los yog local Ollama). This dictates which model handles complex NLP tasks thiab cov ntaub ntawv generation across all cuab yeejs.",
    "header_analytics": "Analytics & Privacy:\nAccess system usage statistics los yog configure telemesim. Kuvn offline los yog FERPA-compliant modes, analytics will be strictly local. This kev pabs track cuab yeej engagement thiab fidelity rau school reporting.",
    "global_mute_toggle": "Universal audio mute hloov. When qhibd, ALL suabs are silenced including: AKuv cov ntawv-to-speech suabs, AlloBot's typing bleeps thiab flub teeb suabs, browser fallrov qab speech, game audio effects, thiab tshaj tawm suabs. Zoo Tag Nrho rau quiet hoobrooms, testing environments, los yog when tub ntxhais kawms xav tau rau work silently. button turns red nrog a pulsing indicator when tab tom khiav. Audio automatically pib duas when koj nyem unmute. This cov teebtings persists across page reloads.",
    "glossary_standard_flashcards": "Launch an intertab tom khiav flashcard study lub session nrog koj cov lus lo luss. Cov Feature: nyem flip (lo lus → lo lus txhais), shuffle mode rau varied practice, kev vam meej tracking (ktsis yogwn vs. learning), audio pronunciation kev xaiv, thiab sequential review. Browse through cards at koj own pace nrog shuffle mode rau variety. XP rewards rau completing study lub sessions. Flashcards auto-khaws kev vam meej—return later rau txuas ntxiv. Luam Tawm physical cards rau offline study. Renrhiav qhias tab tom khiav recall (flashcards) is more effective than passive review rau long-lo lus retention.",
    "glossary_etymology_info": "Qhias each lo lus's origin thiab root components. Zoo Heev rau Tier 3 science/social studies cov lus where Greek/Latin roots (photo-, cardio-, -ology) carry meaning. Two ways rau tsim: (1) hloov 'Kuvnclude lo lus roots' before generating a phau ntawv txhais lus rau tau etymology in one batch, los yog (2) nyem 'Qhia lo lus roots' per-lo lus after generation rau on-demthiab roots. Grade-aware: K-5 taus simple lo lusing like 'comes los ntawm Greek lo lus photo meaning lub teeb', 6-12 taus prefix/root/suffix breakdown nrog source luss. Respects lus lub hom phiaj: glossaries tsimd in Spanish tau Spanish etymologies. Kuvf a lo lus has tsis yog meaningful etymology (proper tsis yogun, recent coinage), feature gracefully hlas it. Roots appear on flashcard rov qabs thiab PDF xa tawms. Lus Pab: etymology is single highest-leverage retention strategy rau domain-specific cov lus.",
    "timeline_visuals_info": "Tsim AKuv icons/illustrations rau each sequence item. Off by default rau khaws generation sij hawm. Zoo Heev rau K-5 thiab EL tub ntxhais kawms who benefit los ntawm visual anchors (photosynthesis stages, life cycles, historical events, size/scale sequences). Ntxivs ~30-50 vib nas ntsivs rau generation rau a 10-item sequence using pooled concurrency (5 at a sij hawm, 3 retries per item). Daim Duabs also appear inside in-game cabgable cards rau dual-coded recall. Per-item daim duabs can be tsim duad los ntawm hloov kho mode. Revising sequence tsos qub daim duabs thiab tsim duas if hloov stays on (since revised items tsis yog longer match qub visuals). Lus Pab: leave off rau abstract sequences (intensity, hierarchy theems) where generic icons can mislead; turn on rau concrete events, objects, thiab procedural steps.",
    "glossary_language_flashcards": "Launch bilingual flashcard practice rau lus learning. Cards qhia: lo lus in lus lub hom phiaj → translation in native lus (or reverse). Audio pronunciation muaj rau both luss. Zoo Tag Nrho for: ELL tub ntxhais kawms learning English cov lus, world lus hoobes, heritage lus maintenance, thiab bilingual education. Cov Feature include: flip direction hloov (L1→L2 los yog L2→L1), pronunciation practice mode, thiab culturally-aware translations. Practice builds: cov lus in concov ntawv, nyeeming fluency in both luss, thiab cross-linguistic connections. Kev Vam Meej syncs nrog regular flashcard mastery—lo luss learned in one mode suav across both.",
    "glossary_export_standard": "Xa Tawm koj cov lus flashcards as a luam tawmable PDF. Output includes: all lo luss thiab lo lus txhaiss, front/rov qab card lakojt, thiab cut lines rau yooj yim separation. Luam Tawm kev xaivs: 4 cards per page (loj, yooj yim rau handle), 8 cards (standard size), los yog 12 (compact). PDF is formatted rau double-sided luam tawming so fronts thiab rov qabs align. Zoo Heev for: offline study, hoobroom teebs, thiab niam txiv homework support. Lus Pab: Luam Tawm on cardstock rau durable physical flashcards.",
