    "tool_faq": "Tsim tub ntxhais kawm-friendly Q&A teebs that anticipate common lo lus nugs thiab misconceptions. AKuv analyzes koj source content rau tsim: comprehension lo lus nugs (What/Who/When), kev tshawb lo lus nugs (Why/How), thiab clarification lo lus nugs (What is difference betpeben...). Each lo lus teb is written at koj tartau qib kev kawm nrog cov lus support. Siv for: study guides, nyeeming comprehension tshawbs, Socratic seminar preparation, los yog tub ntxhais kawm self-assessment. FAQs can be nyeem aloud nrog karaoke-style highlub teebing. Xa Tawm as luam tawmable study sheet los yog intertab tom khiav pebb page.",
