    "tool_persona": "Launch AKuv-popebred character conversations. Xaiv from: historical figures (scientists, leaders, artists), literary characters (from tsis yogvels, ntauss, myths), los yog tsim custom personas. Kuvnterview mode: ask lo lus nugs thiab receive character-autom qabtic responses. Panel mode: xaiv mullus pable personas rau a moderated discussion los yog debate. Characters maintain: period-appropriate ktsis yogwledge, autom qabtic suab thiab perspective, thiab educational accuracy. Zoo Tag Nrho for: exploring primary source perspectives, literature kev tshawb, historical empathy, thiab debate practice. Characters can interact nrog each other when mullus pable are xaived. Lus Pab: Prepare lo lus nugs beforehthiab rau focsivd learning conversations.",
    "tool_concept_sort": "Tsim sorting challenges that develop hoobification skills. AKuv tsims: categories (pawgs rau sorting), items (things rau sort), thiab yog placements. Kev Ua homs: simple sort (one category per item), Venn diagram (overlapping categories), thiab multi-category (3+ pawgs). Cov Teebtingss control: item suav, category complexity, thiab visual style. Sorting builds: critical thinking, compare-contrast skills, thiab conceptual organization. Kuvtems can be: cov ntawv, daim duabs, los yog mixed. Zoo Heev for: cov lus hoobification, concept differentiation, thiab assessment. XP rewards rau accuracy. Lus Pab: Pib nrog simple binary sorts, advance rau Venn diagrams rau more nuanced thinking.",
