    "venn_sorted_item": "An item koj have alnyeemy placed in a category zone. Nyem xaiv it thiab reveal tsiv kev xaivs, los yog cab rau reposition. While learning, feel free rau tsiv items betpeben zones as koj understanding develops. A tshawbmark appears on yogly placed items after tshawbing. Kuvnyogly placed items can be tsivd rau resim. Strategy: place items koj are confident about thawj, tom qab siv those decisions rau inform uncertain placements. Each item contributes rau koj overall accuracy qhab nia. Ua Kom Tiavly sorted diagrams nrog high accuracy earn bonus XP.",
    "venn_bank_item": "Kuvtem tosing rau be hoobified. Located in hqubing bank below Venn diagram. Cab rau appropriate zone: Teeb A (left circle), Teeb B (right circle), los yog Shared (overlapping center). For keyboard sivrs: nyem xaiv, tom qab siv zone buttons rau place. Bank items reprexa tag concepts that xav tau categorization. All items must be placed rau ua kom tiav kev ua. Kuvtems can be returned rau bank if reconsidering. Lus Pab: Nyeem category labels carefully before placing items, thiab consider what uas items similar los yog different.",
