    "venn_move_b": "Place currently xaived item into Teeb B (right circle). Teeb B reprexa tags vib nas ntsiv category in comparison. Kuvtems in Teeb B only: belong exclusively rau this category, do tsis yogt share characteristics nrog Teeb A. Nyem when an item tshemly belongs rau just this pawg. Keyboard accessible. After placing, item appears in Teeb B zone. Can be tsivd again if koj change koj mind. Lus Pab: Think about what distinguishes Teeb B los ntawm Teeb A, thiab place items that fit only Teeb B's criteria.",
    "venn_move_shared": "Place currently xaived item in Shared zone (center overlap). Kuvtems in Shared: belong rau BOTH categories, have characteristics of Teeb A AND Teeb B. This is intersection in Venn diagram. Nyem when an item fits both pawgs criteria. Shared items are often most interesting rau discussion becasiv they bridge categories. After placing, item appears in center. Can be tsivd rau either single teeb if reconsidering. Lus Pab: Shared items are often key concepts that connect ideas across categories.",
