    "word_sounds_review_delete_word": "Permanently tshem tawm this lo lus los ntawm current Lo Lus Suabs lub session. Siv when: lo lus does tsis yogt fit lus qhia objectives, lo lus is inappropriate rau tub ntxhais kawm population, los yog koj xav a shorter kev ua. Deletion is immediate thiab cantsis yogt be untiav—if koj might xav lo lus later, consider moving it rau end instead. Minimum lo lus suav is 3 rau a valid kev ua. Deleting below minimum will prompt koj rau ntxiv more lo luss before pibing. Lo Lus suav adjusts automatically after deletion. Lus Pab: Tshem after reviewing all lo luss tab sis before pibing kev ua nrog tub ntxhais kawms.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_word": "Preview how this lo lus will be protsis yogunced during kev ua. Audio sivs koj current Suab cov teebtingss (suab xaivion, ceev, suab nrov). Mloog to: verify pronunciation is yog rau koj dialect, assess if ceev is appropriate rau koj tub ntxhais kawms, thiab practice koj own pronunciation before leading instruction. Nyem mullus pable sij hawms rau repeat. Audio is same as tub ntxhais kawms will hear during cov kev ua thiab on flashcards. Kuvf pronunciation seems wrong, tshawb if lo lus has mullus pable pronunciations (nyeem vs. nyeem) thiab consider ntxiving phonetic lus pabs in lo lus spelling.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_phonemes": "Hear each individual suab in lo lus spoken separately, tom qab blended. For lo lus CAT: koj hear /k/... /æ/... /t/... tom qab cat. This demonstrates phoneme segmentation (breaking lo luss into suabs) thiab blending (combining suabs into lo luss)—two pomational skills rau nyeeming. Ceev adjusts automatically rau learner theem. Builds phonemic awareness, single strongest predictor of early nyeeming ua tau. Siv for: phonics instruction, photsis yoglogical awareness intervention, thiab kev pabing struggling nyeemers connect letters rau suabs. Renrhiav qhias explicit phoneme instruction improves decoding skills.",
    "word_sounds_review_image_gen": "Tsim a visual reprexa tagation of this cov lus lo lus using AKuv daim duab generation. Daim Duabs support cov lus acquisition by connecting lo luss rau concrete visuals (dual coding theory). For abstract lo luss, AKuv tsims mekovhorical los yog concov ntawvual daim duabs. Art style follows koj current Daim Duab Style cov teebtings. Daim Duabs appear in Lo Lus Suabs cov kev ua, flashcards, thiab luam tawmable materials. Tsim Dua if daim duab does tsis yogt tshemly reprexa tag concept los yog koj xav variety. Lus Pab: Siv consistent art styles within a lus qhia rau visual coherence. Daim Duabs can be rub tawmed rau siv in other materials.",
