    "word_sounds_review_distractor_input": "Customize lo lus teb choices rau rhyming cov kev ua. For Rhyme Sij Hawm: enter yog rhyming lo lus thiab distractor kev xaivs that do tsis yogt rhyme. Distractors should be: phonetically similar tab sis tsis yogt true rhymes (tsims productive challenges), age-appropriate cov lus, thiab distinct etsis yogugh rau avoid confusion about yog lo lus tebs. Zoo distractors test whether tub ntxhais kawms understthiab rhyming patterns versus surface similarity. Koj can tsim dua AKuv-suggested distractors los yog tsim koj own. Lus Pab: Siv distractors that share consonants tab sis differ in vopebls rau specifically tartau rhyme discrimination skills.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_distractor": "Hear how this distractor lo lus suabs before using it in kev ua. Audio preview kev pabs verify: pronunciation is tshem, lo lus is distinguishable los ntawm tartau, thiab audio quality is acceptable. Siv rau tshawb that tub ntxhais kawms will be able rau hear difference betpeben yog rhymes thiab distractors. Kuvf pronunciation is untshem los yog too similar rau tartau, consider choosing a different distractor. Audio sivs koj current Suab cov teebtingss. Preview all distractors rau ensure kev ua audio is consistent thiab tshem rau koj tub ntxhais kawms.",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Sau a thoughtful reflection after koj conversation nrog historical/fictional character. Prompts guide reflection on: What surprised koj? What did koj learn? How did this change koj thinking? Reflections are assessed using koj learning objectives thiab earn XP based on depth thiab connection rau content. Tab Tom Sau develops metacognition (thinking about thinking) thiab consolihnubs learning. AKuv provides feedrov qab on reflection quality. Reflections are khawsd rau tub ntxhais kawm portfolio thiab can be shared nrog xib fwbs. Lus Pab: Encourage tub ntxhais kawms rau cite specific moments los ntawm conversation in their reflection.",
