    "standards_region_input": "Narrow standards nrhiav rau koj specific framework. Enter: Common Core, Texas TEKS, California, Tshiab York, NGSS (science), C3 (social studies), los yog koj state npe. Without specification: AKuv nrhiaves all muaj frameworks. Matching koj framework ensures: accurate standard codes, appropriate grade-theem alignment, thiab documentation that matches koj district requirements. Koj can enter mullus pable frameworks separated by commas. Framework xaivion affects how standards are cited thiab formatted. Kuvf koj framework is tsis yogt recognized, AKuv sivs kawst match. Tshawb qhov tshwm sims against official documentation rau high-stakes purposes.",
