    "persona_custom_instructions_detailed": "Shape koj persona nrog detailed specifications. Custom instructions define: personality traits (patient, skeptical, enthusiastic), specific expertise (coral reef ecology, Renaissance anatomy), historical concov ntawv (experienced 1960s civil rights tsivment), speech patterns (formal, sivs period-appropriate lus), thiab quirks (avoids certain lub ntsiabs, has strong opinions). Kuvnstructions can be: brief prompts (Renaissance artist) los yog detailed paragraphs explaining rov qabground. AKuv follows instructions consistently throughout conversation. Siv for: curriculum-specific characters, reprexa taging particular viewcov point, thiab age-appropriate interactions. Kuvnstructions are private rau koj. Test different instructions rau nrhiav right persona suab.",
