    "quiz_reflection_count": "Ntxiv qhib-response lo lus nugs that require written explanations, tsis yogt just lo lus teb xaivion. These lo lus nugs: assess deeper understanding beyond recognition memory, build metacognitive skills (explain koj thinking), provide insight into tub ntxhais kawm reasoning, thiab prepare tub ntxhais kawms rau extended writing tasks. Each reflection lo lus nug includes a rubric-aligned prompt. AKuv tsims lo lus nugs that connect rau source content thiab learning objectives. For formative assessment, 1-2 reflection lo lus nugs provide valuable insight. For summative, 2-3 tsim balanced assessment of both ktsis yogwledge thiab application.",
