    "adventure_custom_instructions": "Provide specific guidance rau shape AKuv Game Master tus cwj pwm. Examples: Cov Teebtings details (Teeb in ancient Rome during Punic Wars), Content focus (Kuvncorporate cov lus los ntawm our unit on ecosystems), Character traits (Ua mentor character patient thiab encouraging), Pedagogical lub hom phiajs (Kuvnclude decision cov point that require mathematical reasoning), Thematic elements (Emphasize themes of cooperation thiab community). AKuv follows these instructions when generating story content, dialogue, thiab choices. Siv for: curriculum alignment, cov lus reinforcement, SEL themes, thiab content-specific scenarios. Kuvnstructions can be uphnubd mid-kev mus txawv teb chaws rau evolving focus.",
    "adventure_free_response": "Controls how tub ntxhais kawms interact nrog story. When OFF (default): Tub Ntxhais Kawms xaiv los ntawm 4 AKuv-tsimd kev xaivs each turn—easier rau kojnger learners, ELLs, los yog structured lus qhias. When ON: Tub Ntxhais Kawms hom any action they xav thiab AKuv adapts story—encourages creative writing thiab agency, tab sis narrative may take unexpected turns. Lus Pab rau Xib Fwbs: Pib nrog kev xaivs OFF rau tshiab sivrs, tom qab qhib free response once they understthiab story concov ntawv. Free response mode builds composition skills as tub ntxhais kawms must articulate their intended actions tshemly.",
    "adventure_chance_mode": "Ntxivs tabletop RPG-style dice mechanics rau kev mus txawv teb chaws. When qhibd: risky los yog uncertain actions trigger a D20 roll (visualized on screen). Roll qhov tshwm sims affect outcomes—a 'Nat 20' guarantees ua tau nrog bonus effects, while a '1' casivs humorous failure. This teaches: probability concepts, risk vs. reward decision-making, thiab that outcomes aren't always within our control. Tub Ntxhais Kawms learn rau pelojh odds before acting. Recommended rau grades 4+ who can grasp chance concepts. Tsims exciting 'clutch moments' that ua story memorable!",
