    "adventure_system_state": "Ntxiv khoom siv management mechanics rau kev mus txawv teb chawss. Tub Ntxhais Kawms track: Health (consequence of risky choices), Gqub/Khoom Sivs (ecotsis yogmic decision-making), Reputation (social capital los ntawm choices), thiab custom khoom sivs koj define. Actions affect khoom sivs visibly—spend gqub rau buy items, lose health los ntawm poor decisions, gain reputation los ntawm kev pabing others. Tsims meaningful consequences that teach: casiv-and-effect reasoning, planning ahead, khoom siv management, thiab opportunity cost. Visual dashboard qhias current khoom siv theems. When khoom sivs deplete, game adaptively responds (p.t., low health = limited kev xaivs). Math skills integrate naturally through khoom siv calculations.",
    "glossary_tier2_count": "Teeb how many Tier 2 (academic) cov lus lo luss rau include. Tier 2 lo luss: appear across lub subjects, are sivd in academic concov ntawvs, thiab are esxa tagial rau cov ntawv comprehension. Examples: analyze, evidence, significant, contrast. These lo luss have highest instructional value—most tub ntxhais kawms benefit los ntawm explicit teaching. Recommended suav depends on: cov ntawv length (1 lo lus per 100-150 lo luss of source), muaj instruction sij hawm, thiab tub ntxhais kawm xav tau. Balance nrog Tier 3 suav rau a ua kom tiav cov lus teeb. Focus instruction here rau maximum impact on nyeeming comprehension across all lub subjects.",
    "glossary_tier3_count": "Teeb how many Tier 3 (domain-specific) cov lus lo luss rau include. Tier 3 lo luss: are specific rau a lub subject area, are usually defined in concov ntawv, thiab may tsis yogt transfer across lub subjects. Examples: photosynthesis, detsis yogminator, alliteration, legislative. These lo luss are esxa tagial rau understanding specific content tab sis have limited siv outside domain. Kuvnstruction typically occurs during content teaching. For deep dive into a lub ntsiab, include more Tier 3. For broader nyeeming skills, prioritize Tier 2. Tier 3 lo luss often appear in bqub los yog italics in cov ntawvbooks, signaling their coj tuajance within discipline.",
    "glossary_definition_level": "Control how lo lus txhaiss are written. Kev Xaivs: Same as Source (maintains original complexity—zoo rau advanced tub ntxhais kawms), On Grade (matches tartau qib kev kawm cov lus), Simplified (sivs common lo luss, shorter xa tagences), thiab Kindergarten (very basic lus, concrete examples). Match lo lus txhais complexity rau tub ntxhais kawm theem nyeem, tsis yogt content theem. A 10th-grader studying advanced biology might xav tau Simplified lo lus txhaiss rau unfamiliar lo luss. Consider koj tub ntxhais kawms pebakest nyeemers when xaiving. Lo Lus Txhaiss can be individually hloov khoed after generation if some xav tau adjustment. Pro lus pab: Siv Simplified initially, tom qab discuss more technical lo lus txhaiss in hoob.",
