    "simplified_format": "Change structure thiab style of cov ntawv while keeping content. Kev Xaivs include: Narrative (standard prose), Dialogue (conversation format), Tshiabs Article (journalistic style nrog headline), Social Media (thnyeem format nrog emoji), Comic Script (panel kev piav qhias), Poem (poetic structure), Kuvnterview (Q&A format), thiab Letter (personal correspondence). Format changes can increase engagement by prexa taging familiar content in tsis yogvel ways. Some formats work better rau certain content homs. Tub Ntxhais Kawms often nrhiav Dialogue thiab Social Media formats more accessible. Xib Fwbs can siv different formats rau teach genre conventions. All formats maintain core learning content.",
