    "simplified_citations": "Maintain academic integrity by preserving source attribution. When qhibd: hyperlinks remain nyemable, citation formats are preserved (APA, MLA, thiab lwm yam), footcov tsis yogte are retained, thiab source references stay intact. Esxa tagial for: renrhiav papers, academic cov ntawvs, thiab verifiable content. Citations appear in adapted format appropriate rau theem nyeem. Link cov ntawv may be simplified while URLs remain kev uaal. Bibliography sections are preserved tab sis may be reformatted rau clarity. Kaw only rau creative adaptation where source attribution is tsis yogt xav taued. Supports: academic honesty education, renrhiav skills, thiab source evaluation. Lus Pab: Always preserve citations rau factual content.",
    "simplified_charts": "Transform cov ntawvual cov ntaub ntawv into visual reprexa tagations. AKuv identifies: numerical cov ntaub ntawv, relationships, processes, thiab comparisons in koj cov ntawv, tom qab tsims appropriate visualizations. Output formats: cov ntaub ntawv tables (organized ntaub ntawv), flowcharts (processes), comparison charts (differences/similarities), thiab sij hawmlines (sequences). Mermaid.js format qhibs: intertab tom khiav pebb disntaus, yooj yim hloov khoing, thiab mullus pable xa tawm kev xaivs. Zoo Heev for: visual learners, cov ntaub ntawv comprehension, thiab making abstract concepts concrete. Charts can be tsim duad nrog different styles. Hloov Kho tsimd charts rau refine accuracy. Lus Pab: Complex cov ntawvs often contain zais tag cov ntaub ntawv that charts can reveal.",
