    "scaffolds_type": "Xaiv scaffqub format that best supports koj learning objective. Xa Tagence Pibers: provide pibning of thoughts rau tub ntxhais kawms rau ua kom tiav (main idea is..., This reminds me of...). Paragraph Frames: offer structured templates nrog blanks rau full paragraph construction. Discussion Prompts: qhib-ended lo lus nugs that guide verbal los yog written exploration. Xaiv based on: tub ntxhais kawm skill theem (pibers are most supportive), task hom (writing vs. haising), thiab independence lub hom phiaj (frames build toward independent writing). Mix homs within a lus qhia rau varied support. Lus Pab: Pib nrog more structured scaffqubs thiab gradually tshem tawm supports as tub ntxhais kawms develop skills.",
