    "brainstorm_simulation_type": "Xaiv collaborative thinking structure. Kev Xaivs include: Socratic Bridge (guided lo lus nuging toward understanding), Rolentaus (assume perspectives rau explore issues), Think-Pair-Share (structured peer discussion), Debate (argue opposing viewcov point), thiab more. Each hom develops different skills: Socratic builds critical thinking, Rolentaus develops empathy, Debate strengtom qabs argumentation. AKuv facilitates chosen routine nrog appropriate prompts thiab responses. Xaiv based on: learning objective, content hom, thiab skills rau develop. Mullus pable simulations can be khiav on same content. Lus Pab: Match simulation hom rau cognitive skills koj xav tub ntxhais kawms rau practice.",
