    "timeline_topic": "Specify a different focus rau sij hawmline generation. By default: AKuv extracts primary lub ntsiab los ntawm koj cov ntawv hauv paus. Override to: narrow focus rau specific aspect, broaden rau related concov ntawv, los yog redirect rau connected lub ntsiab. Examples: Kuvf source is about WWKuvKuv, override rau Battle of Midway rau specific focus, los yog Casivs of WWKuvKuv rau analytical sij hawmline. Custom lub ntsiabs still draw los ntawm source content where relevant. Leave blank rau siv AKuv-detected lub ntsiab. Custom lub ntsiab must be related rau source rau coherent qhov tshwm sims. Lus Pab: Siv custom lub ntsiabs rau tsim mullus pable sij hawmlines los ntawm same source nrog different focsivs.",
