    "outline_structure": "Xaiv visual organization pattern. Kev Xaivs include: Traditional Outline (hierarchical nrog Roman numerals), Venn Diagram (compare/contrast), Flow Chart (sequential processes), Concept Map (interconnected ideas), Casiv-Effect Chart (causal relationships), thiab more. Xaiv based on: content structure (sequential, comparative, relational), learning objective, thiab tub ntxhais kawm xav taus. Each structure highlub teebs different relationships in content. Some structures work better rau certain content homs. AKuv adapts content rau fit chosen structure. Mullus pable structures can be tsimd los ntawm same content. Lus Pab: Match structure rau how koj xav tub ntxhais kawms rau think about relationships in content.",
