    "venn_item_bank": "Unsorted items tosing rau be placed in Venn diagram. Each item reprexa tags a concept that xav taus hoobification. Nyeem carefully rau delo lusine whether it belongs to: Teeb A only, Teeb B only, los yog Both (intersection). Cab items rau their destination zones, los yog siv keyboard controls (Tab rau xaiv, tom qab siv A/B/Shared buttons). Kuvtems can be repositioned if koj change koj mind. Work through systematically—placing one item often gives lus pabs about others. All items must be placed before tshawbing lo lus tebs. Remaining suav qhias how many are left rau sort.",
