    "venn_drop_zone_b": "Right circle zone rau items exclusive rau Category B. Kuvtems placed here should have attributes that define Teeb B tab sis lack defining attributes of Teeb A. Think carefully about what uas something belong ONLY here thiab tsis yogt in intersection. Example: Kuvf sorting Fiction vs. Tsis Yognfiction, a biography goes in Tsis Yognfiction-only zone becasiv it is factual thiab tsis yogt fictional. Common mistake: placing items here that actually have some Teeb A characteristics too, which should go in intersection. Review koj placement before tshawbing lo lus tebs. Consider specific criteria being tested by category labels.",
