    "fab_toggle": "Qhia los yog zais floating accessibility button panel. When visible: quick access rau focus cuab yeejs, dictation, sij hawmrs, thiab nyeeming aids. When zais tag: cleaner screen nrog more content space. FAB (Floating Action Button) provides one-nyem access rau frequently sivd accessibility features without navigating menus. Position can be tsivd by cabging. FAB remembers position across lub sessions. Contains: focus spotlub teeb, line ruler, dictation, sij hawmr, thiab customizable shortcuts. For minimal distraction, zais FAB thiab siv keyboard shortcuts instead. Recommended: keep visible rau tub ntxhais kawms using accessibility cuab yeejs regularly.",
