    "visuals_download": "Rub Tawm daim duab rau koj device. File khawss as high-resolution PNG rau koj Rub Tawms fquber. Full generation resolution is preserved. Siv rub tawmed daim duabs for: luam tawming, prexa tagations, worksheets, thiab external projects. Daim Duab is immediately muaj in koj system Rub Tawms fquber. Filenpe includes descriptive cov ntawv los ntawm prompt. Mullus pable rub tawms tsim tus naj npawbed files. Rub Tawmed daim duabs are independent copies (deleting los ntawm gallery does tsis yogt affect rub tawmed files). PNG format works everywhere: pebb, luam tawm, documents. Lus Pab: Rub Tawm daim duabs koj xav rau keep permanently since cloud storage may have limits los yog expiration.",
    "visuals_prompt": "See thiab modify generation prompt. Qhias: original prompt cov ntawv, cov teebtingss sivd (style, quality), thiab generation sij hawmstamp. Hloov Kho prompt to: refine details, change style, fix issues, los yog tsim variations. Modified prompts tsim tshiab daim duabs (original is preserved). Siv for: iterating on a concept, adjusting style, thiab learning what prompts work pebll. Prompt keeb kwm kev pabs understthiab what lus produces zoo qhov tshwm sims. Theej prompt rau resiv in tshiab concov ntawvs. Long prompts can be trimmed rau esxa tagials. Lus Pab: Me prompt changes often produce significantly different qhov tshwm sims—experiment rau learn AKuv art prompting.",
    "visuals_refiner": "Qhib daim duab enhancement studio. Refiner allows: style changes (ua more realistic, more cartoonish, change art style), detail ntxivitions (ntxiv more rov qabground detail, enhance faces), thiab specific fixes (tshem tawm an element, change xims). Describe what koj xav changed in natural lus. AKuv modifies existing daim duab rather than creating tshiab los ntawm scratch. Refinement sivs ntxivitional APKuv crhloov khos beyond original generation. Mullus pable refinement passes are possible. Each refinement tsims a tshiab version (original preserved). Quality of refinement depends on clarity of koj instructions. Lus Pab: Siv specific kev piav qhias like ua sky more dramatic los yog ntxiv more detail rau trees rau best qhov tshwm sims.",
    "visuals_regenerate": "Tsim a fresh daim duab nrog same prompt cov teebtingss. AKuv produces a tshiab variation. Tsims a ua kom tiavly different daim duab even though prompt is identical. Siv when: current daim duab is tsis yogt quite right, koj xav kev xaivs rau xaiv from, los yog koj xav tau variety. Original daim duab is preserved. tsim dua rau build a collection of kev xaivs. Each regeneration sivs APKuv crhloov khos. More specific prompts produce more consistent qhov tshwm sims; general prompts produce more variation. Lus Pab: Tsim Dua several sij hawms rau nrhiav best daim duab, tom qab tshem ones koj do tsis yogt xav rau conserve storage.",
    "role_teacher": "Ua Kom Tiav platform access rau educators. Xib Fwb role includes: all content generation cuab yeejs, full configuration kev xaivs, tub ntxhais kawm kev vam meej dashboard thiab analytics, lo lus teb keys thiab grading features, permission management rau tub ntxhais kawm access, lub session hosting thiab live monitoring, thiab xa tawm/coj tuaj capabilities. Xib Fwb view qhias: detailed kev pab rau pedagogical best practices, advanced cov teebtingss rau customization, thiab professional features. Passlo lus protection prevents tub ntxhais kawms los ntawm accessing xib fwb features. Xib Fwb acsuavs can: manage mullus pable hoobes, share khoom sivs nrog colleagues, thiab access premium features. Lus Pab: Review Cov Teebtingss rau customize experience rau koj teaching style thiab tub ntxhais kawm xav taus.",
    "role_student": "Age-appropriate learning interface nrog built-in supports. Tub Ntxhais Kawm role includes: simplified cuab yeej xaivion, gamified XP thiab achievement system, theem nyeem adaptation, thiab structured kev ua flow. Cov Feature are: xib fwb-controlled (some kaw rau focus), kev vam meej-tracked (visible in dashboard), thiab scaffqubed (appropriate support theems). Kuvnterface qhias: tshem navigation, friendly icons, thiab encouraging feedrov qab. Tub Ntxhais Kawm cantsis yogt access: lo lus teb keys, detailed analytics, los yog configuration cov teebtingss. Kev Vam Meej syncs rau xib fwb dashboard. XP motivates engagement. Achievements celebrate milestones. Lus Pab: Ua Kom Tiav cov kev ua rau earn XP thiab unlock rewards while learning content.",
    "role_parent": "Family-centered experience rau home learning support. Niam Txiv role includes: child kev vam meej visibility, age-appropriate interface lus, co-learning kev ua kev xaivs, thiab home-school connection features. Cov Feature are: designed rau tsis yogn-educators, supportive of niam txiv involvement, thiab privacy-conscious. Kuvnterface sivs: accessible lus avoiding EdTech jargon, tshem explanations of cov kev ua, thiab positive framing of kev vam meej. Niam Txiv can: view (tsis yogt hloov kho) tub ntxhais kawm work, participate in cov kev ua alongside child, thiab communicate nrog xib fwbs (if connected). Does tsis yogt include: grading features, hoob management, los yog detailed analytics. Lus Pab: Siv niam txiv mode rau stay involved in koj child education thiab support learning at home.",
    "role_independent": "Adult learner los yog self-guided mode. Full access rau all features without restrictions. Kev Vam Meej tracking is personal thiab tsis yogt shared externally. Suitable for: adult learners, independent study, thiab home siv without oversight. Cov Feature: all cuab yeejs muaj, tsis yog permission restrictions, self-managed pacing, thiab private analytics. Does tsis yogt sync rau any xib fwb dashboard. XP thiab achievements are personal. Content is tsis yogt filtered by qib kev kawm. Siv for: professional development, personal enrichment, thiab unrestricted exploration. This mode trusts sivr rau manage their own learning experience thiab teeb appropriate boundaries.",
    "ui_language_select": "Teeb disntaus lus rau all UKuv elements. Tsodown qhias: pre-txhaisd luss (immediate), recently tsimd luss (if any), thiab kev xaiv rau tsim tshiab translations. Xaiving a lus uphnubs: all buttons, menus, labels, cov luss, thiab kev pab cov ntawv. Kuvnterface lus is separate from: content generation lus (teeb in cuab yeejs) thiab TTS suab lus (teeb in Suab Cov Teebtingss). This allows: Spanish xib fwb using English interface, English interface generating Mandarin content, thiab lwm yam Some technical lo luss remain in English when tsis yog translation exists. Lus preference khawss rau koj profile. Lus Pab: Teeb interface lus rau match koj preferred working lus rau easiest navigation.",
