    "entry_start_new": "Pib a brthiab tshiab lub session nrog tsis yog tom qab cov ntaub ntawv loaded. Siv when: pibning a tshiab lub ntsiab, working nrog different tub ntxhais kawms, los yog xaving a clean slate. Pibing tshiab does tsis yogt tshem koj keeb kwm—tom qab lub sessions remain accessible via Keeb Kwm panel. Koj can load prior lub sessions anysij hawm. Tshiab lub sessions: tsim fresh workspace, pib dua kev vam meej tracking, thiab pib nrog tsis yog source content. Koj cov teebtingss thiab preferences persist (theme, suab, thiab lwm yam). Tshiab lub sessions automatically khaws after initial content is ntxived. Lus Pab: Pib tshiab when changing lub ntsiabs rau keep keeb kwm organized by lub subject.",
    "entry_load_exist": "Pib Dua koj tom qab lub session nrog all cov ntaub ntawv intact. Tab Tom Load restores: XP earned, kev ua kev vam meej, khawsd responses, cov teebtingss preferences, thiab lub session keeb kwm. Zoo Tag Nrho for: multi-hnub projects, continuing interrupted work, thiab maintaining momentum. Koj most recent lub session loads by default. To load a different lub session, siv Keeb Kwm panel. Cloud sync ensures cov ntaub ntawv is muaj on any device. Tab Tom Load replaces any current unkhawsd work. Kuvf koj made changes, khaws thawj los yog they will be lost. XP thiab streaks txuas ntxiv los ntawm where koj left off. Lus Pab: Always load existing lub session when returning rau hoob rau maintain continuity thiab tub ntxhais kawm motivation.",
    "teacher_gate_modal": "Security gate protecting xib fwb-only features. Appears when: tub ntxhais kawms sim rau access cov teebtingss, view lo lus teb keys, change configurations, los yog access analytics. Tub Ntxhais Kawms cantsis yogt bypass this gate. Xib Fwbs: enter koj passlo lus rau unlock full kev uaality. Passlo lus is teeb during acsuav creation los yog by school administrator. Kuvf koj have forgotten koj passlo lus, contact koj admin los yog siv pib dua kev xaiv in Cov Teebtingss. gate protects: lo lus teb keys, grading cuab yeejs, lub session controls, content hloov khoing, thiab tub ntxhais kawm cov ntaub ntawv. Gate sij hawmout re-locks after 30 feebs of inkev ua rau security.",
    "teacher_gate_input": "Enter koj xib fwb passlo lus rau unlock protected features. Passlo lus requirements: 4-8 characters, case-sensitive. Kuvnyog attempts: 5 attempts before temporary lockout. Kuvf kaw out los yog forgotten: contact koj school admin los yog siv passlo lus recovery in Cov Teebtingss. Passlo lus is separate los ntawm koj login credentials rau ntxivitional security. Consider: using a memorable tab sis tsis yogt obvious passlo lus, changing passlo lus periodically, thiab tsis yogt sharing nrog tub ntxhais kawms. gate prevents accidental los yog intentional tub ntxhais kawm access rau sensitive features. Xib Fwb passlo luss are encrypted thiab never visible rau admins—only pib duatable.",
    "teacher_gate_unlock": "Xa passlo lus rau verification. Kuvf yog: xib fwb features unlock, gate disappears, koj have full access until sij hawmout. Kuvf inyog: yuam kev cov lus qhias, attempts suaver decrements, resim los yog pib dua. Once unkaw: access cov teebtingss, view lo lus teb keys, see tub ntxhais kawm cov ntaub ntawv, change configurations, thiab siv grading cuab yeejs. Unlock persists rau current lub session los yog until 30-feeb inkev ua sij hawmout. Re-unlock after sij hawmout by entering passlo lus again. For convenience, qhib Remember on this device in cov teebtingss (reduces re-autom qabtication on trusted devices). Lus Pab: Unlock before hoob pibs rau avoid delays during instruction.",
    "submit_confirm_btn": "Final submission of koj ua kom tiavd work. Before nyeming: review all responses, tshawb rau ua kom tiavness, thiab verify koj are nyeemy rau xa. After submission: work is kaw (tsis yog further hloov khos), xib fwb is tsis yogtified, sij hawmstamp is recorded, thiab koj XP is finalized. Kuvf koj xav tau rau ua changes after xating, ask koj xib fwb rau return koj work rau revision. Returned work can be hloov khoed thiab rexated. Submission is final rau current attempt—treat it as turning in a paper hauj lwm. Lees Paubation dialog appears before submission rau prevent accidental nyems. Take a breath thiab review before lees paubing.",
    "mastery_draft_input": "Sau koj response demonstrating understanding of learning objective. Koj draft is evaluated against mastery criteria. Sau tshemly thiab ua kom tiavly since this contributes rau koj mastery assessment. Drafts can include: main idea explanations, evidence nrog reasoning, connections rau prior ktsis yogwledge, thiab application examples. Auto-khaws preserves koj work as koj hom. Lo Lus suav thiab basic metrics disntaus as koj sau. Suab dictation muaj via FAB microphone. Xib Fwb sees drafts in real-sij hawm during live lub sessions. Mullus pable drafts can be khawsd thiab compared. Focus on qhiaing what koj understand, tsis yogt just right lo lus tebs. Quality over length.",
    "faq_edit_toggle": "Switch betpeben view thiab hloov kho modes rau FAQ content. When ON (Xib Fwb Mode): nyem any Q&A rau hloov kho cov ntawv, ntxiv tshiab lo lus nugs nrog + button, tshem irrelevant pairs, thiab reorder rau logical flow. When OFF: nyeem-only disntaus as tub ntxhais kawms see it. Hloov Khos khaws automatically. Siv hloov khoing to: yog AKuv-tsimd content, ntxiv lo lus nugs tub ntxhais kawms actually ask, tshem tawm confusing los yog redundant items, thiab customize rau koj specific tub ntxhais kawms. All changes are versioned—undo muaj. Tub Ntxhais Kawm view is kaw rau prevent tampering. Lus Pab: Review AKuv-tsimd FAQs thiab hloov kho rau accuracy before sharing nrog tub ntxhais kawms.",
