    "tool_read_mode": "Default nyeeming mode nrog standard cov ntawv disntaus. Cov Feature: tsis yogrmal cov ntawv prexa tagation, keyboard navigation (arrow keys scroll), thiab standard cov ntawv xaivion. Nyeem Mode is baseline—tsis yog special intertab tom khiav features tab tom khiav. Siv when: tub ntxhais kawms are nyeeming independently without supports, content is at appropriate theem, los yog koj xav distraction-free cov ntawv. Other modes (Define, Phonics, Explain) ntxiv interkev ua tab sis may slow nyeeming rau fluent nyeemers. Hloov modes anysij hawm without losing place. Nyeem Mode works nrog all accessibility cov teebtingss (theme, overlays, font). Most lub teebpelojht mode rau slopebr devices los yog when maximum focus is xav taued.",
