    "adventure_immersive_toggle_ui": "Hloov UKuv visibility during kev mus txawv teb chaws. When zais tag: maximum story immersion, fullscreen narrative, minimal distraction. When qhian: access rau all controls, cov teebtingss, thiab inventory. Hloov anysij hawm during ntaus. Zais Tag mode is zoo heev for: nyeeming focus, prexa tagations, thiab cinematic experience. Visible mode xav taued for: cov teebtingss access, inventory management, thiab xib fwb controls. Story txuas ntxivs tsis yogrmally in both modes. Keyboard shortcut muaj. Touch edges rau reveal UKuv when zais tag. Lus Pab: Zais UKuv when tub ntxhais kawms are nyeeming, qhia when making choices los yog tshawbing inventory.",
    "adventure_immersive_exit": "Leave fullscreen immersive experience. Nyeming exits to: standard kev mus txawv teb chaws view, visible controls, thiab tsis yogrmal interface. Kev Mus Txawv Teb Chaws txuas ntxivs los ntawm current position. Kev Vam Meej is preserved. Siv when: xav tauing rau access cov teebtingss, switching cov kev ua, los yog ua tiaved ntausing. Kuvmmersive mode can be re-entered anysij hawm. Exit does tsis yogt end kev mus txawv teb chaws. Keyboard shortcut: Escape key also exits. Lus Pab: Exit immersive mode when koj xav tau rau kev pab tub ntxhais kawms los yog access xib fwb controls.",
