    "adventure_immersive_inventory": "Access collected items while in immersive view. Kuvnventory qhias: all items acquired during kev mus txawv teb chaws, item kev piav qhias thiab sivs, thiab current khoom siv suavs. Kuvtems may be: usable (consumables), key items (story-coj tuajant), los yog equipment (stat-affecting). Nyem items rau siv los yog inspect. Kuvnventory management is part of gamentaus in System Simulation mode. Some items are yuav tsum muaj rau kev vam meej. Lus Pab: Tshawb inventory regularly rau remember what khoom sivs koj have muaj rau solving challenges.",
    "adventure_choice_toggle": "Expthiab rau qhia muaj kev xaivs. Nyem reveal 4 AKuv-tsimd choices rau current story beat. Choices are: concov ntawvually appropriate, varied in approach, thiab balanced in outcome potential. Zais again by nyeming. Choice visibility can be controlled by xib fwb. Tub Ntxhais Kawm can request different kev xaivs. Each choice leads rau unique story continuation. Choices include: dialogue kev xaivs, actions, thiab decisions. Lus Pab: Nyeem all choices before xaiving rau nrhiav one that best matches koj intent.",
    "adventure_choice_btn": "Lees Paub this choice rau advance narrative. Nyeming: xas koj decision, tsims story continuation, thiab prexa tags tshiab scene thiab choices. Decision is logged rau xib fwb review. XP may be awarded based on choice quality. Story adapts rau koj decision. Some choices have immediate consequences; others affect later story. Choices cantsis yogt be untiav without xib fwb intervention. AKuv remembers all tom qab choices rau narrative consistency. Lus Pab: Consider consequences before choosing, especially in challenging nyuaj modes.",
