    "adventure_art_style": "Art Style Xaivion:\nXaiv visual art style rau AKuv-tsimd kev mus txawv teb chaws illustrations. Kev Xaivs include Auto (lets AKuv pick), Storybook (hoobic children's illustration), Waterxim, Anime, Pixel Art, thiab more. Different styles tsim different atmospheres rau story — Storybook works pebll rau kojnger nyeemers, while Anime los yog Pixel Art may engage quber tub ntxhais kawms. style applies rau all scene illustrations in kev mus txawv teb chaws.",
    "adventure_consistent_characters": "Consistent Characters Feature:\nWhen qhibd, AKuv will attempt rau maintain same visual appearance rau characters across all scenes in koj kev mus txawv teb chaws. This means hero, companions, thiab recurring characters will look same in every illustration, creating visual continuity. This sivs reference-based daim duab generation — thawj scene establishes each character's look, thiab subsequent scenes sim rau match it. Zoo Heev rau narrative comprehension thiab character tracking.",
    "adventure_setup_chk_consistent_characters": "Hloov Consistent Characters:\nTshawb this box rau qhib persistent character visuals throughout koj kev mus txawv teb chaws story. When tab tom khiav, AKuv tsims a character reference sheet los ntawm thawj scene thiab sivs it rau maintain visual consistency in later illustrations. This is especially kev pabful rau kojnger nyeemers who rely on visual cues rau track characters across scenes. Can be kawd if koj prefer more artistic variety betpeben scenes.",
    "dashboard_export_research_btn": "Xa Tawm Renrhiav PDF:\nTsim a professional APA-formatted renrhiav report los ntawm koj tub ntxhais kawm cov ntaub ntawv. PDF includes: cov ntaub ntawv summary tables, statistical analyses, trend visualizations, thiab properly formatted citations. Designed for: educators conducting action renrhiav, school psychologists preparing reports, graduate tub ntxhais kawms documenting intervention outcomes, thiab administrators reviewing program effectiveness. report follows academic formatting standards suitable rau publication los yog prexa tagation.",
    "immersive_chunk_reader": "Chunk Nyeemer Mode:\nBreaks passage into individual xa tagences los yog me chunks that are revealed one at a sij hawm. Navigate mus pem hauv ntej thiab rov qabward through chunks at koj own pace, los yog qhib auto-ntaus rau automatic kev vam meejion. This reduces visual overwhelm rau struggling nyeemers by limiting visible cov ntawv rau a single manageable piece. Renrhiav supports chunked nyeeming rau improving comprehension, reducing anxiety, thiab building fluency. Pairs pebll nrog cov ntawv-to-speech rau multi-modal support.",
    "bl_data_insights": "Cov Ntaub Ntawv Kuvnsights Panel:\nAKuv-tsimd kev tshawb of koj collected tus cwj pwmal cov ntaub ntawv. Qhias top tus cwj pwmal patterns (most common antecedent-tus cwj pwm chains), peak risk sij hawms (when tus cwj pwms occur most frequently), thiab an overall narrative summary. Uphnubd automatically as koj ntxiv more ABC entries. Siv these insights rau identify kev ua hypotheses, establish baseline patterns, thiab guide intervention planning. Cov Ntaub Ntawv stays entirely local — tsis yog tub ntxhais kawm ntaub ntawv leaves koj browser.",
    "bl_interval_recording": "Kuvnterval Recording:\nA systematic kev soj ntsuam cuab yeej rau collecting sij hawm-based tus cwj pwmal cov ntaub ntawv. Supports three indussim-standard methods: Whole Kuvnterval (tus cwj pwm must occur rau entire interval), Partial Kuvnterval (tus cwj pwm occurs at any point during interval), thiab Momentary Sij Hawm Sampling (tus cwj pwm observed at exact moment interval ends). Configure interval duration (5-120 vib nas ntsivs), lub session length, thiab tartau tus cwj pwms. Produces percentage-of-intervals cov ntaub ntawv suitable rau graphing thiab kev vam meej monitoring.",
