    "bl_data_triangulation": "Cov Ntaub Ntawv Triangulation:\nCross-references mullus pable cov ntaub ntawv sources rau strengtom qab reliability of koj kev uaal tus cwj pwm assessment. Combines ABC narrative records, interval recording cov ntaub ntawv, thiab direct kev soj ntsuams rau look rau convergent evidence. When mullus pable cov ntaub ntawv methods point rau same tus cwj pwmal kev ua, confidence in koj hypothesis increases. Triangulation is a BACB best-practice requirement rau defensible FBAs thiab is often cited in KuvEP documentation.",
    "bl_datasheet_generator": "Cov Ntaub Ntawv Sheet Generator:\nTsims luam tawmable, structured cov ntaub ntawv collection sheets tailored rau koj chosen measurement method. Supports: frequency/event recording, duration recording, interval recording (partial, whole, MTS), thiab latency recording. Each sheet includes: tub ntxhais kawm npe, hnub fields, tartau tus cwj pwm lo lus txhaiss, recording grid, thiab space rau cov tsis yogte. Luam Tawm directly los ntawm browser los yog khaws as PDF. Designed rau match paper forms school psychologists thiab BCBAs typically siv in practice.",
    "bl_practice_sandbox": "Practice Sandbox:\nA safe training environment rau learning tus cwj pwmal cov ntaub ntawv collection thiab kev tshawb without using real tub ntxhais kawm cov ntaub ntawv. Xaiv los ntawm pre-built scenarios (escape, attention, tangible, sensory) los yog tsim custom AKuv scenarios nrog configurable parameters. Zoo Tag Nrho for: pre-service xib fwb training, professional development workshops, BCBA fieldwork practice, thiab learning cuab yeej before working nrog actual tub ntxhais kawms. All sandbox cov ntaub ntawv is tshemly labeled as mock/fictional.",
    "bl_data_quality_checker": "Cov Ntaub Ntawv Quality Tshawber:\nAnalyzes koj ABC cov ntaub ntawv collection rau ua kom tiavness, specificity, thiab adherence rau best practices. Tshawbs for: missing fields (blank antecedents, consequences), vague tus cwj pwmal kev piav qhias (p.t., 'was phem' vs. 'threw materials'), insufficient entries rau reliable kev tshawb, thiab unbalanced cov ntaub ntawv collection across sij hawm periods. Provides a quality qhab nia thiab specific actionable recommendations. Kev Pabs ensure koj cov ntaub ntawv is defensible thiab sivful rau FBA/BKuvP development.",
    "bl_trend_dashboard": "Tus Cwj Pwm Trend Dashboard:\nVisualizes temporal patterns in koj ABC cov ntaub ntawv. Qhias: daily/pebekly frequency charts, tus cwj pwm intensity heat maps, sij hawm-of-hnub distribution graphs, thiab kev ua hypothesis breakdown over sij hawm. Look rau acceleration (increasing) los yog deceleration (decreasing) trends rau evaluate intervention effectiveness. Kuvncludes split-middle trend lines thiab theem changes betpeben baselines thiab intervention phases. Xa Tawm charts rau inclusion in KuvEPs los yog kev vam meej reports.",
    "bl_aba_graph_engine": "ABA Graph Engine:\nTsims publication-standard single-case design graphs following ABA conventions. Supports: A-B designs, A-B-A-B withdrawal, mullus pable baseline across tus cwj pwms/cov teebtingss/participants, alternating treatment, thiab changing criterion designs. Cov Feature: phase change lines, trend lines, aim stars, condition labels, thiab cov ntaub ntawv path markers. Graphs follow standards yuav tsum muaj rau JABA publication thiab BACB exam preparation. Xa Tawm as PNG los yog SVG rau reports.",
    "bl_dtt_data_sheet": "DTT Cov Ntaub Ntawv Sheet:\nDiscrete Trial Training cov ntaub ntawv collection cuab yeej rau structured skill-acquisition programs. Tsim mullus pable programs (tartaus), define mastery criteria (p.t., 80% across 3 lub sessions), thiab record trial-by-trial cov ntaub ntawv (+, -, P rau prompted). Automatic mastery detection advances rau tom ntej tartau. Tracks: thawj-trial yog cov ntaub ntawv, yuam kev patterns, prompt hierarchy theems, thiab cumulative performance graphs. Designed rau BCBAs khiavning intensive teaching programs.",
    "bl_latency_recorder": "Latency Recorder:\nMeasures elapsed sij hawm betpeben a stimulus (instruction los yog environmental cue) thiab onteeb of a tartau tus cwj pwm. Kov 'Pib' when koj give instruction, kov 'Response' when tus cwj pwm pibs. Records latency in vib nas ntsivs nrog millivib nas ntsiv precision. Sivful for: measuring compliance ceev, tracking response sij hawm improvements during skill acquisition, thiab documenting delays that may indicate processing difficulties. Cov Ntaub Ntawv feeds into koj ABC record thiab graphs.",
    "bl_natural_language_abc": "Natural Lus ABC Ensim:\nHom los yog tso koj kev soj ntsuam cov tsis yogte in everyhnub English thiab let AKuv structure them into formal ABC (Antecedent-Tus Cwj Pwm-Consequence) entries. Example: 'During math, Johnny was asked rau ua kom tiav worksheet, threw his pencil thiab yelled, xib fwb redirected him rau quiet corner' → AKuv extracts: Antecedent: Academic demthiab (math worksheet), Tus Cwj Pwm: Threw pencil + verbal outburst, Consequence: Redirection rau quiet area. Khawss sij hawm thiab uas cov ntaub ntawv collection accessible rau paraprofessionals thiab general education xib fwbs.",
    "bl_caseload_dashboard": "Caseload Dashboard:\nBird's-eye view of koj entire tub ntxhais kawm caseload nrog status indicators thiab trends. Qhias: each tub ntxhais kawm's cov ntaub ntawv recency (how fresh their cov ntaub ntawv is), trend direction (improving, stable, worsening), intervention phase, thiab tag nrho entries. Xim-coded alerts highlub teeb tub ntxhais kawms who xav tau attention — p.t., insufficient recent cov ntaub ntawv, concerning upward trends, los yog approaching KuvEP review hnubs. AKuv provides a caseload summary highlub teebing priority tub ntxhais kawms.",
    "bl_ai_observation_coach": "AKuv Kev Soj Ntsuam Coach:\nReceive real-sij hawm AKuv coaching on quality of koj tus cwj pwmal cov ntaub ntawv collection. coach reviews koj ABC entries thiab provides feedrov qab on: specificity of tus cwj pwmal kev piav qhias, balance of cov ntaub ntawv across sij hawm periods, adequate capture of antecedent details, variety of consequence documentation, thiab inter-observer agreement suggestions. Rates koj cov ntaub ntawv collection quality on a scale thiab provides actionable lus pabs rau improvement. Kuvdeal rau tshiab practitioners building kev soj ntsuam skills.",
    "bl_voice_to_abc": "Suab-to-ABC:\nHais koj tus cwj pwmal kev soj ntsuams naturally using koj device's microphone. AKuv transcribes thiab automatically structures koj speech into formal ABC entries. Zoo Tag Nrho for: recording kev soj ntsuams in real-sij hawm during challenging moments when typing isn't feasible, hands-free cov ntaub ntawv collection during physical interventions, thiab quick in-the-moment documentation. Supports natural lus like 'During recess, Marcus hit a peer after being tqub he couldn't siv swing, xib fwb implemented planned igtsis yogring.' Transcript reviepebd before saving.",
    "quiz_pedagogical_mode_select": "Xaiv pedagogical intent of this quiz. Exit Ticket: end-of-lus qhia tshawb rau understanding (default). Pre-Tshawb: probe what tub ntxhais kawms alnyeemy ktsis yogw before teaching, surfaces gaps as concept cards nrog one-nyem 'Explain rau hoob' AKuv broadcasts. Formative Tshawb: 1-3 quick items mid-instruction nrog a real-sij hawm yog/inyog heatmap. Spaced Review: probes tom qably-taught concepts thiab tracks each tub ntxhais kawm's cross-lub session retention nrog a per-concept sparkline. Each mode tunes prompts, item-hom mix, thiab live dashboard lakojt. Lus Pab: Pre-Tshawb before teaching unlocks just-in-sij hawm hoob explainer flow.",
    "quiz_visual_mode_select": "Tsim AKuv daim duabs rau MCQ items. Tsis Yogne: cov ntawv only, fastest, free. Lo Lus Nug daim duabs: one daim duab per lo lus nug stem (5 MCQs = 5 daim duabs, ~5-8s wall-clock). Kev Xaiv daim duabs: 4 daim duabs per lo lus nug, one per lo lus teb choice (~10-15s). Both: lo lus nug stimulus + 4 kev xaiv thumbnails per MCQ. All daim duabs are stored as base64 nrog quiz, can be refined in place via pencil overlay in hloov kho mode, thiab a Style lus pab below this tsodown applies rau every tsimd daim duab consistently.",
